  24 Mar 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org>
  bibletime-1.4.2_pre1.ebuild:
  added ~amd64 to KEYWORDS, fixes #86435

  06 Sep 2004; Ciaran McCreesh <ciaranm@gentoo.org>
  bibletime-1.4.2_pre1.ebuild:
  Switch to use epause and ebeep, bug #62950

  06 Jul 2004; Joel Martin <kanaka@gentoo.org> bibletime-1.4.2_pre1.ebuild:
  RDEPEND was incorrectly marked as DEPEND causing dependencies to be ignored.
  Changed DEPEND to RDEPEND.

  06 Jul 2004; Carsten Lohrke <carlo@gentoo.org> bibletime-1.4.2_pre1.ebuild:
  QA: newdepend -> R/DEPEND, need-kde

  02 Jul 2004; Jon Hood <squinky86@gentoo.org> -bibletime-1.3.ebuild,
  -bibletime-1.4.1.ebuild, bibletime-1.4.2_pre1.ebuild:
  stable on x86, remove old non-working versions

